{"tid":1990113,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【泛民議員請入】警方指抱有共同聚集目的已屬公眾地方群組聚集","createTime":"2020-04-26T12:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T13:24:27.000Z","uid":230298,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c422f9f2d9fee0f093b8cbeec2c03c6a8896cb3b","tid":1990113,"uid":230298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"// 有指，只要四人或以下參與公眾活動，而且與其他參與公眾活動人士保持1.5米距離，便不會違反第599G章。警方嚴正澄清，任何出席公眾活動人士，如抱有共同聚集目的，均屬於公眾地方進行羣組聚集；而該公眾活動如有多於四人參與，所有參與者均屬違反第599G章。而羣組聚集者是否相距1.5米，都會違反第599G章。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-8-11_RB7C5_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FUntitled-8-11_RB7C5_1200x0.png&h=600c0dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/04/20200411_PO_%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A43.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F04%2F20200411_PO_%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A43.jpeg&h=a1986b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://n.kinliu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/mfile_1521479_1_L_20200419163134-1-768x509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.kinliu.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fmfile_1521479_1_L_20200419163134-1-768x509.jpg&h=5e9e1193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果少數派窮追盲打陳淑莊，呢到有李梓敬、華記正撚樣係到，大家唔係唔識做呀？"},{"pid":"6ade25f4e30edd68bec6d23a4a49027501a70d0a","tid":1990113,"uid":230298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1417b1b785ad0d397fc26ee45e42aa94edfb85","tid":1990113,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"去任何商店買嘢都唔可以超過四個人，因為大家都有買嘢嘅共同目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor